    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a reliable daily driver for someone who doesn't mind a bit of character. While the engine and transmission are functional, you can expect some cosmetic wear such as minor dents, paint fading, and interior upholstery thinning. It has been regularly serviced, though it will likely need some routine maintenance like new tires or brake pads in the near future. Overall, it is a solid, honest car that reflects its age and mileage but still has plenty of life left in it.",
