      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle represents a premier opportunity for the discerning driver. Demonstrating consistent mechanical integrity and a refined aesthetic, it has been preserved to ensure a sophisticated driving experience. Its performance remains robust, and the interior reflects a high standard of care. We invite you to acquire this distinguished model, which exemplifies a harmonious balance of luxury, reliability, and enduring value.",
